Name: Kaede the Eliminator / Eliminator 小枫
About the game: The self-proclaimed most indecent TPS (third-person shooting) game in Japan. The silver-haired girl simply blasts away at unfamiliar creatures with her gun! Shoot down enemies over and over in the Survival Mode. Target enemies within a specific time frame in the sniper mode. Includes 3 mini-games where you complete 10 stages within a time limit. The Survival Mode has items such as a turret to put you at an advantage! Functions that allow you to change outfits and enjoy 'special actions' is also included.
